acetic acid as having mild antibacterial and

00:02:07.361 --> 00:02:12.410
antifungal properties, which is why vinegar
can be used as a mild household cleanser…

00:02:12.410 --> 00:02:16.060
But putting vinegar on your face is probably
not the best idea.

00:02:16.060 --> 00:02:21.620
